headline: Aon's Quarterly Earnings Preview: What You Need to Know
summary: Aon is expected to announce its third-quarter results before the end of October, and analysts project a notable single-digit growth in earnings.

headline: OpenAI, Anthropic eye investor funds to settle AI lawsuits, FT reports
summary: Kevin Kalinich, head of cyber risk at Aon, told the newspaper that the insurance sector broadly lacks "enough capacity for (model) providers."  OpenAI has considered "self-insurance" by setting aside investor funding, with discussions about establishing a "captive," a ringfenced insurance vehicle used by large companies to manage emerging risks, the report said.
